    "index.content3.subtitle": "The story of Dr. Osaze - March 2024 ",
    "index.content3.subtitle1": "You will sleep and wake up, and you will not find stammering again.",
    "index.content3.subtitle2":
      "God spoke these words to Dr. Osaze through His servant. Though he initially laughed in disbelief, a month later, he woke up speaking fluently after nearly 40 years of severe stammering. Three medical professional colleagues confirmed this miracle, and his mother wept with joy, hearing her son speak clearly for the first time.",
    "index.content4.subtitle": "JESUS FEST Kuopio - June 2024",
    "index.content4.subtitle1": "Did you like the book? Yes, I read it last night.",
    "index.content4.subtitle2":
      "'And he said unto them, Go ye into all the world, and preach the gospel to every creature.' Deliverance from terrible nightmares, crowds standing for hours in the cold and rain to listen, and attendees devouring a 100+ page event gift book in a single night between event days—this is just a glimpse of what transpired.",
    "prayer.herotext.tagline": "Prayer",
